<item>
            <title>[LU-18179] Implementation of Round-Robin/Fair Share response with Token Bucket Filters</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-18179</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently, it appears that CRRN, TRR, and ORR must be selected separately from Token Bucket FIlters.&#160; It might be considered an improvement to have the Round Robin responses, from the Lustre servers to clients while also implementing TBFs.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="84229">LU-18179</key>
            <summary>Implementation of Round-Robin/Fair Share response with Token Bucket Filters</summary>
